text
@To enable bitlbee you have to add a line like:

127.0.0.1:6667    stream  tcp     nowait _bitlbee ${PREFIX}/libexec/bitlbee bitlbee

to your /etc/inetd.conf and restart inetd with

# kill -HUP `cat /var/run/inetd.pid`
